text: Mikheil Babunashvili (born 31 May 1996) is a Georgian Rugby Union player. His position is Flanker and he currently plays for RC AIA Kutaisi in the Georgian championship and the Georgia U20 team.http://www.worldrugby.org/tournament/1567/teams/2762http://www.rugby.com.au/players/25108 ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Rugby union players from Georgia (country)
